{"tid":1249864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我的爸爸是一名警察","createTime":"2019-06-22T00:11:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T08:49:41.000Z","uid":28007,"like":2639,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"9c2f2dae995054ffb7eaeb620c707d0fb24009be","tid":1249864,"uid":28007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T00:11:43.000Z","msg":"沒有爸爸的第7天 晴<br />\n<br />\n今天 我在無線電視新聞台看到很多香港市民在街上<br />\n我不知道發生什麼事<br />\n只是最近爸爸都不怎麼回家<br />\n所以我和媽媽很是擔心<br />\n<br />\n直到我看到電視螢幕上<br />\n那強壯的臂彎<br />\n熊厚的厚肌<br />\n英傻的外表<br />\n<br />\n是爸爸！<br />\n<br />\n我很興奮 立即把衣衫不整的媽媽從漆黑中的房間裡拉出來<br />\n一起見證爸爸成為萬眾矚目的一刻<br />\n<br />\n可是媽媽只是說了一句：「那可恨的一哥 竟把你爸爸放在危險的前線」<br />\n<br />\n說罷 便拉著剛剛她帶回家的叔叔 一起回房間<br />\n<br />\n爸爸 弟弟快要出生了<br />\n所以你回來了沒？我很想念你<br />\n<br />\n我不喜歡那一個叔叔 <br />\n你快點回來把他趕走吧<br />\n<br />\n而且誰是一哥 為什麼媽媽不喜歡他？"},{"pid":"d875199205907d54153d37deb56637c59d161979","tid":1249864,"uid":216800,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T00:13:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2104a2ec2ed2366df0aa9b9492045189cfef8e34","tid":1249864,"uid":202730,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T00:16:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好"},{"pid":"614d7829495b2e989e1ce740bfd09067756bd2dc","tid":1249864,"uid":27038,"like":841,"dislike":1,"score":840,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T00:19:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18676d51e0acfbc3be951ecd9f17887d296fd866","tid":1249864,"uid":28007,"like":432,"dislike":2,"score":430,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T00:25:51.000Z","msg"