484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T03:57:36.000Z","msg":"睇到扯左"},{"pid":"3e7c99e36e1557b232339643dd30b40331308e98","tid":1249864,"uid":169965,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"9c2f2dae995054ffb7eaeb620c707d0fb24009be","tid":1249864,"uid":28007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T00:11:43.000Z","msg":"沒有爸爸的第7天 晴<br />\n<br />\n今天 我在無線電視新聞台看到很多香港市民在街上<br />\n我不知道發生什麼事<br />\n只是最近爸爸都不怎麼回家<br />\n所以我和媽媽很是擔心<br />\n<br />\n直到我看到電視螢幕上<br />\n那強壯的臂彎<br />\n熊厚的厚肌<br />\n英傻的外表<br />\n<br />\n是爸爸！<br />\n<br />\n我很興奮 立即把衣衫不整的媽媽從漆黑中的房間裡拉出來<br />\n一起見證爸爸成為萬眾矚目的一刻<br />\n<br />\n可是媽媽只是說了一句：「那可恨的一哥 竟把你爸爸放在危險的前線」<br />\n<br />\n說罷 便拉著剛剛她帶回家的叔叔 一起回房間<br />\n<br />\n爸爸 弟弟快要出生了<br />\n所以你回來了沒？我很想念你<br />\n<br />\n我不喜歡那一個叔叔 <br />\n你快點回來把他趕走吧<br />\n<br />\n而且誰是一哥 為什麼媽媽不喜歡他？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:19:01.000Z","msg":"6月9日，那夜爸爸不在家，亦是叔叔第一次來的日子。<br />\n<br />\n那晚飯後，媽媽一如以往地督促我趕功課。<br />\n<br />\n「叮，你有一個新口訊。」<br />\n<br />\n「叮，你有兩個新口訊。」<br />\n<br />\n「叮，你有三個新口訊。」......<br />\n<br />\n電話劃破寂靜。<br />\n<br />\n「媽，爸爸有口訊俾你。」<br />\n<br />\n「嗯！媽媽入房打電話比爸爸，你要乖乖地做功課，知道嗎?」<br />\n<br />\n「知道。」我爽快地答。<br />\n<br />\n媽媽雙手握著電話，兩步并作兩步的奔向睡房。<br />\n<br />\n「我也想知道爸爸對媽媽說什麼。」這時我已把右耳貼著爸媽睡房房門，屏住呼吸，全神貫注地偷聽著爸媽的對答。<br />\n<br />\n「哦......好衰架......」媽媽輕聲地說。"},{"pid":"ae53e284c093bb1ab790c1b77b72cd0519c1af7c","tid":1249864,"uid":52939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61952211a8fe3ace4cd9ab115043e5c5079726de","tid":1249864,"uid":28007,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"af021188a152dee5d7720a1dc6b97c4e8c891380","tid":1249864,"uid":52939,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T01:33:23.000Z","msg":"傻瓜 不只一個叔叔啊 我也是其中一個"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T02:14:01.000Z","msg":"那你跟我媽媽房間在做什麼？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:23:59.000Z","msg":"做一次性交清債務的事"},{"pid":"538d80cb9ccb4b31c54bb75345d2bba335172c97","tid":1249864,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:24:58.000Z","msg":"Diu你玩埋日本果D 細思極恐style文學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f305e4cb8e1d2eb91d54ef4a2957e5cbcd7490f","tid":1249864,"uid":14888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:42:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34f7c1aed9a44d4937304fabd71941de7c6a466f","tid":1249864,"uid":266578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:45:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://files.rei.idv.tw/thumb/older/349731b3b4bca4fcb5510c4795898c00.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffiles.rei.idv.tw%2Fthumb%2Folder%2F349731b3b4bca4fcb5510c4795898c00.jpg&h=06ed09f7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"38c1965f8affd19ff2a00ff4121dc8643f269512","tid":1249864,"uid":266578,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:46:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/UrkGulf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FUrkGulf.jpg&h=f907d28d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b32a5faf149cff5b19218a333ef03e0c4753ef76","tid":1249864,"uid":43330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:46:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1d88fbfec63cf882f717b06fb1054d9386c1c8b","tid":1249864,"uid":28007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:06:14.000Z","msg":"好掛住爸爸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99a405934357956c810b4494dcb5f7763b1b77e6","tid":1249864,"uid":106937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:23:33.000Z","msg":"push push psuh"},{"pid":"51f141e7d3ca62595c5f7c5590f96285ef8d